98struct NISLANDS_SMC_HW_PERFORMANCE_LEVEL
99{
100 uint8_t arbValue;

102 uint8_t displayWatermark;

110 NISLANDS_SMC_SCLK_VALUE sclk;
111 NISLANDS_SMC_MCLK_VALUE mclk;
112 NISLANDS_SMC_VOLTAGE_VALUE vddc;
113 NISLANDS_SMC_VOLTAGE_VALUE mvdd;
114 NISLANDS_SMC_VOLTAGE_VALUE vddci;
115 NISLANDS_SMC_VOLTAGE_VALUE std_vddc;
116 uint32_t powergate_en;
117 uint8_t hUp;
118 uint8_t hDown;
119 uint8_t stateFlags;
120 uint8_t arbRefreshState;
121 uint32_t SQPowerThrottle;
122 uint32_t SQPowerThrottle_2;
123 uint32_t reserved[2];
124 PP_NIslands_Dpm2PerfLevel dpm2;
125};
